{"type": "article", "id": 57135, "title": "Banksy 自毁画作后，宜家、麦当劳都出了模仿款海报 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-10-10T05:36:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 4585, "name": "芭比娃娃"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 738, "name": "麦当劳"}, {"id": 48537, "name": "拼多多"}, {"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 3344, "name": "美泰"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1375, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181010130326d4qyMOT6xwEuRbzF.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4292802240298374?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=108A093010&amp;sourcetype=weixin&amp;featurecode=newtitle\" rel=\"nofollow\">朱一龙代言膳魔师</a>，</strong>推广膳魔师十二星座的新品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181010130641gzY2keMZGdpLWBOf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.778261\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4293256282413477\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>景甜担任凡士林品牌身体护理系列代言人。</strong></a>同时，景甜拍摄了新品牌的广告片。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u0739s6iepw\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4293309461967895?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=108A093010&amp;sourcetype=weixin\" rel=\"nofollow\">假笑男孩 Gavin 拍摄海飞丝洗发水广告</a>，</strong>令人疑惑的是，为什么是防脱洗发水？假笑男孩拍摄的海飞丝广告片<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av32031901\" rel=\"nofollow\">在 B 站上</a>可看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=c073936bz51\"></iframe> </figure> </div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/p/searchall?containerid=231522type%3D1%26q%3D%23%E8%B0%A2%E8%B0%A2%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%8B%BC%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%A0%23%26t%3D10&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B0%A2%E8%B0%A2%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%8B%BC%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%A0%23&amp;luicode=20000061&amp;lfid=4293228968912549&amp;featurecode=newtitle\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>拼多多庆祝 10 月 10 日三周年典礼</strong></a>，主题是“谢谢每一个拼过的你”。拼多多拉来施华蔻、匹克、Baseus 倍思等品牌，还拉来了莫文蔚、黄子韬、朱正廷、周迅、周冬雨、胡一天、江一燕、Angelababy 等明星制作海报。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018101012340256BOf71sHLgC0Pwk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.795491\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201810101234039bluwZmrYE5oh7i1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.946667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181010123402LUZlEY0zR2wVrTQg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.795491\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/creativity/mcdonalds-agencies-rush-to-reference-banksys-shredded-painting-with-fry-art/\" rel=\"nofollow\">涂鸦艺术家 Banksy 自毁画作后，麦当劳、宜家都做了模仿海报。</a></strong>TBWA\\ANG、澳洲 DDB 维也纳办公室分别在 Instagram、Facebook 等平台上发布了模仿“自毁画作”的海报，主角是麦当劳的薯条。宜家与代理商 SMFB 合作，</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181010123510gQf3D8wHoCJEmnp2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><p>图片来自：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ddbwien/photos/a.498013523625362/1976205459139487/?type=3&amp;theater\" rel=\"nofollow\">DDB 维也纳@Facebook</a></p></figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201810101235116vdiC7TwMcnzWUR8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><p>图片来自：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BopMSV1A0X-/?taken-by=maltesecreative\" rel=\"nofollow\">TBWA\\ANG@Instagram</a></p></figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201810101235373aO57AiHTUYbGFe4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/nike-late-bloomer-film/\" rel=\"nofollow\">图片来自：ikeanorge@Instagram</a></strong></p></figcaption> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/nike-late-bloomer-film/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>耐克发布新的广告片 <em>Late Bloomer</em></strong></a>，主角是一位 81 岁的马拉松跑者，住在纽约的 Marjorie。这是耐克 Just Do It 广告语 30 周年活动的一部分。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v07390sms6b\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong>匡威发起新的“真的有故事”campaign，主打的是经典鞋款&nbsp;Chuck Taylor All Stars。</strong>匡威与亚太地区 2 位品牌代言人——音乐制作人张艺兴与大提琴演奏家欧阳娜娜，以及三位来自校园的年轻学生， 拍摄了他们与这款鞋的故事。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181010131453jOhxTAnZuNCJGbI6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181010131956zhxHG0bEjn38fl2w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.805238\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=q07397idv6g\"></iframe> </figure>  </div><p><strong>Zippo 在万圣节推出 3 款骷髅重甲机火机</strong>，还挺有节日气氛的<strong>。</strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181010131223lVTUr2sx3o0IebDB.png\" data-ratio=\"0.673932\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181010131241MhY8vkiUpTW3OBd5.png\" data-ratio=\"0.679066\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/10/09/intel-names-denstu-aegis-network-global-media-agency\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>英特尔任命电通安吉斯为全球媒介代理</strong></a>，负责该公司的数字、社交、搜索、程序化、分析与线下媒介账户。电通安吉斯组建了新的 Team Intel 专组。</p><p><br></p><p>题图来自：YouTube@<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_-Ke871DXWU\" rel=\"nofollow\">耐克</a></p>"}